---
description: Theme + language toggles behavior
globs:
  - "src/**/*.{ts,tsx}"
alwaysApply: true
---

Theme toggle:
- Always visible top-right.
- Toggle data-theme on <html> or <body>.
- Persist preference in localStorage.
- Respect prefers-color-scheme on first load.

Language toggle (ES/EN):
- Always visible top-right next to theme toggle.
- Use react-i18next useTranslation().
- Persist chosen language in localStorage.
- Default language: "es" with fallback "es".
- All user-facing strings must come from i18n JSON files (no hardcoded UI text).

Accessibility:
- Buttons must have aria-label.
- Ensure focus styles are visible.
